======================================================================
                             REQUIREMENTS
======================================================================

Before installing,  please make sure  that you have  already installed
the following packages:

  * bison
  * libbison-dev
  * build-essential
  * flex
  * libgmp-dev
  * libmpc-dev
  * maxima
  
  
Additionally, install:
  * NTL 11.1.0 available here: https://shoup.net/ntl
  * barvinok (the latest release) available here: 
             https://repo.or.cz/barvinok.git

======================================================================
                               BUILD
======================================================================

$make

Binaries of the textual converters used in TRAHRHE are generated.

